body_html:
Did you build the toco library using bazel? What worked for me is (from within the TF repo folder)

bazel build tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco:toco

bazel-bin/tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco/toco --help

Did you build the toco library using bazel? What worked for me is (from within the TF repo folder)

`bazel build tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco:toco`

`bazel-bin/tensorflow/contrib/lite/toco/toco --help`
